{
  "chapter": 9,
  "chapter_summary": "第九回\"赤子之心\"讲述了裴珏在失去两本书后的孤独旅程。千手书生的银衫身影与偷书人的突袭交织，裴珏坠马后茫然独行至镇江。在市集中，他偶遇一位以铜镯煮汤的奇特少年，两人虽言语不通，却因真诚与默契结为知己。少年以三指挟沸锅的惊人武功令裴珏惊叹，二人共饮女儿红，在醉意与泪水中倾吐各自的身世悲怆。裴珏在地上写下\"劝君更进一杯酒，与尔同消万古愁\"，少年则回应\"酒逢知己干杯少\"，两个孤独少年在暮色中找到了彼此，心胸滚烫如初。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_shuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "肥硕妇人",
      "listener": "char_tong_luo_shao_nian",
      "text": "少年人，你这是在干什么呀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_luo_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "铜镯少年",
      "listener": "char_fei_shuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "煮汤。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_shuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "肥硕妇人",
      "listener": "char_tong_luo_shao_nian",
      "text": "煮汤？用这只铜镯煮汤？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_luo_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "铜镯少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要是有些葱姜就好了，不过——没有也没有关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_shuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "肥硕妇人",
      "listener": "char_tong_luo_shao_nian",
      "text": "我想……我不知道……再放一点青菜是不是好吃些？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_luo_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "铜镯少年",
      "listener": "char_fei_shuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "无所谓。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "人群",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你闻闻，这味道多香，你知不知道，这是铜镯煮出来的汤。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_luo_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "铜镯少年",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你要不要来尝尝我这锅铜镯煮成的汤，保险比老母鸡煮的汤还好吃。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_luo_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "铜镯少年",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "原来兄台不愿在这么多俗人面前，和——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_tong_luo_shao_nian",
      "text": "劝君更进一杯酒，与尔同消万古愁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_luo_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "铜镯少年",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "酒逢知己干杯少，来！再喝一口。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_luo_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "铜镯少年",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你为什么有那么多伤心的事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    }
  ],
